name: Pork Loin Cuts - Boneless Sirloin
description: Daily total pounds, low price, high price and weighted average price from the USDA LM_PK602 report published by the USDA Agricultural Marketing Service (AMS). This dataset covers Loin Cuts - Boneless Sirloin. Historical figures from USDA can be verified using the LMR datamart located at http://mpr.datamart.ams.usda.gov.
